title 'Afterschool 1'
description_short "Short course designed for informal learning"
description "Afterschool 1 is designed to for informal classrooms where students vary in age, and assessment is not required. This course focuses on learning through entertainment with varying options for implementation, all in 10 sessions or less. Students are encouraged to complete all puzzles, but the overall progression allows for learning in as few as six puzzles per stage. Use alone or with Afterschool Unplugged. Recommended for grades 3-8."
description_audience "Ages 7-13"
